義肢裝具學實習                           PROSTHETICS AND ORTHOTICS PRACTICE


  	This course contains two parts---prosthetics and orthotics for upper extremity. The lectures introduces basic features, constructions, types, check-out and training programs in prosthetics. The indications, designing and fabricating of splints and orthoses will also be illustrated. Furthermore, the general concepts of L/E and other orthoses will be included. The practice, going along with the topics of  lectures, will provide substantial operation in clinical usage. We hope the students of occupational therapy will get more understandings and experiences about prosthetics and orthotics in this course. This course contains two parts---prosthetics and orthotics for upper extremity. The lectures introduces basic features, constructions, types, check-out and training programs in prosthetics. The indications, designing and fabricating of splints and orthoses will also be illustrated. Furthermore, the general concepts of L/E and other orthoses will be included. The practice, going along with the topics of  lectures, will provide substantial operation in clinical usage. We hope the students of occupational therapy will get more understandings and experiences about prosthetics and orthotics in this course. 

課程教育目標 

A 培育具有專業知能的職能治療人才 Train occupational therapy experts with professional knowledge.B 培育具有人本關懷的職能治療人才 Train occupational therapy experts with humanity caring.C 培育具有主動求知、終身學習及貢獻科學研究之發展的職能治療人才 Train occupational therapy experts with active asking, lifelong learning, and science research contribution. 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

A 職能治療專業知識與理論
具備職能治療專業知識理論基礎，以為專業技能奠基。
B 職能治療專業技能
具備職能治療專業技能，以提供個案職能表現之評估、分析與治療的能力。
C 溝通表達及團隊合作之能力
培養適切溝通表達及團隊合作能力，以建立良好的醫病關係及專業團隊互動。
D 獨立思考及問題解決之能力
培養具有獨立思考、臨床推理及問題解決的能力，並能終身學習。

